<chapter xml:id="doing-reproducible-research">
  <title>Doing reproducible research</title>
  
  <introduction>
    <p>
      This chapter covers principles and practices for conducting reproducible statistical research.
    </p>
  </introduction>

  <section xml:id="reproducibility-crisis">
    <title>The reproducibility crisis</title>
    <p>
      Many scientific findings have failed to replicate, highlighting the importance of reproducible research practices.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section xml:id="best-practices">
    <title>Best practices for reproducible research</title>
    <p>
      Following best practices helps ensure that research can be verified and built upon.
    </p>
  </section>
</chapter>
